            "title": "從玉智農澄清配股價變更為0.565元 股份午後復牌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">從玉智農(00875)發公告澄清，配股協議應是在上周五收市後訂立，配股價變更為0.565元，較上周五收市價折讓19.29%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司今次配股集資淨額約4230萬元，約2500萬元用於採購，約1400萬元用於償還其他借款及其他應付款，約330萬元用於一般營運資金。該公司股份今午復牌。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14728684-%e5%be%9e%e7%8e%89%e6%99%ba%e8%be%b2%e6%be%84%e6%b8%85%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e8%ae%8a%e6%9b%b4%e7%82%ba0-565%e5%85%83-%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%bd%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%be%a9%e7%89%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/00875-Web.jpg.webp",
