        {
            "title": "滬深股指早市好淡爭持 高盛唱好料A股未來3個月反超港股",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">儘管高盛唱好內地A股，滬深兩市今早仍只能呈好淡爭持局面，AI芯片概念股寒武紀(0688256.SH)則創新高。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"寒武紀官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/688256.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"寒武紀官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/688256.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">寒武紀官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">高盛昨天發報告，認為在估值優勢及政策預期支持下，滬深A股有在未來3個月內反超港股，取得約2%的超額回報。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早低開5點後，暫時卻僅呈好淡拉鋸爭持，半日高位3384點時僅升5點，低位3361點時則跌17點；滬指中午收報3375點，反覆微跌3點或0.11%，半日成交則達5478.55億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指略為跑贏，今早高開3點後初段跌幅雖然曾擴大至48點，低見10942點，但早市大部份時間仍維持升市，高位11045點，曾漲54點；深指中午收報10989點，微跌1點或0.02%，成交8685.94億元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數跌4點或0.11%，收報3974點；創業板指數跌18點或0.79%，報2263點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">芯片股個別發展，寒武紀(688256.SH)曾創新高，最高衝上795.8元，升7.22%；中午收報778元，仍漲4.82%。華虹(01347)A股(688347.SH)微升0.54%，報60.1元；相反，中芯(00981)A股(688981.SH)則微跌0.75%，報103.2元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14728370-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e6%8c%87%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e5%a5%bd%e6%b7%a1%e7%88%ad%e6%8c%81-%e9%ab%98%e7%9b%9b%e5%94%b1%e5%a5%bd%e6%96%99a%e8%82%a1%e6%9c%aa%e4%be%863%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e5%8f%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250206_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-24 11:40:38",
